ropic hydrodynamic vortex, increases monotonically\nwith increasing values of the integer harmonic index $m$ and decreasing values\nof the dimensionless polytropic index $N_{\\text{p}}$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 6 Nov 2017 19:00:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-11-22"}
