.\nWe also insist on the crucial impact of the star's rotation on the observables.\nFinally, we close a controversy that has been appearing in the literature in\nthe recent years regarding the validity of the ATM24 code.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 7 Nov 2017 11:39:09 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 21 Feb 2018 09:21:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-03-28"}
