ased on a large fraction of the archival transit light curves\nused in our analysis. The unusual profile of this transmission spectrum is\npoorly matched by theoretical spectra and is not confirmed by more recent\nobservations at higher spectral resolution. Additional data, both in emission\nand transmission, are required to better constrain the atmospheric properties\nof WASP-103 b.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 7 Nov 2017 15:45:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-12-27"}
